.DT
brief
Discworld player help
brief

.SH Name
.SI 5
brief - brief mode control
.EI

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
brief [type|all]
.EI

.SH Description

.SP 5 5
The brief command controls which things you see in brief mode and which in verbose.  Typing just 'brief' will list which items are in which state.  Typing 'brief all' will set all items to brief.

In brief mode you will get reduced descriptions of events depending on which items you have in brief mode.
.EP

.SH Examples
.SI 5
> brief
Your settings are: combat (verbose) look (brief) score (verbose) names (verbose)
> brief combat
Ok.
> brief all
Ok.
.EI

.SH See also
.SI 5
verbose
.EI
